    GxpInstance

    public class Gxp
extends AbstractGxp<com.google.gxp.html.HtmlClosure>
    Struts 2 to GXP adapter. Can be used to write a GXP or create a HtmlClosure. Pulls GXP parameters from Struts 2 value stack.
